data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: What I can see from the picture is that there is a blue racing car trying to go back onto the track. The car has a lot of paint sprayed all over it, showing the sponsors behind the car racing team. A huge tailfin is mounted onto the tail of the car, supposedly to perform some kind of aerodynamic function – preventing the car from being lifted by strong air streams generated while the car runs extremely fast. I can tell, from the direction of its front left wheel, that the car is turning left. Since half of the car is off the grey asphalt track, I suppose that the driver probably somehow made a mistake. Beside the track, there is a lawn on which piles of white tyres are placed. (131字)
